---
title: "checkUpkeep (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_paused: check contract paused
    q_paused --> [*]: paused == true; return (false, empty)
    q_paused --> q_asset_out: paused == false

    q_asset_out --> [*]: s_assetOut not configured; return (false, empty)
    q_asset_out --> q_access: s_assetOut configured

    q_access --> [*]: caller lacks AUCTION_WORKER_ROLE; return (false, empty)
    q_access --> q_iter: caller has AUCTION_WORKER_ROLE

    q_iter --> q_check_end: for asset in s_allowlistedAssets
    q_iter --> q_build_result: all assets processed

    q_check_end --> q_mark_ended: auction exists AND (elapsed >= duration OR balance < minAuctionSize)
    q_check_end --> q_check_start: no ended auction for asset

    q_mark_ended --> q_iter: add asset to endedAuctions list

    q_check_start --> q_iter: asset not configured (soft skip)
    q_check_start --> q_check_price_out: asset configured

    q_check_price_out --> q_iter: assetOut price stale or zero (soft skip, zeros eligible list)
    q_check_price_out --> q_check_price_in: assetOut price valid

    q_check_price_in --> q_iter: asset price stale or zero (soft skip)
    q_check_price_in --> q_check_live: asset price valid

    q_check_live --> q_iter: live auction exists for asset (soft skip)
    q_check_live --> q_check_min: no live auction

    q_check_min --> q_iter: totalUsdValue < minAuctionSizeUsd (soft skip)
    q_check_min --> q_add_eligible: totalUsdValue >= minAuctionSizeUsd

    q_add_eligible --> q_iter: add asset to eligible list

    q_build_result --> [*]: return (hasWork, abi.encode(eligible, ended))

    note right of q_check_start
        INV-005: checkUpkeep uses soft-skip (not revert) for ineligible assets
        INV-006: totalUsdValue includes balance in both FeeAggregator and auction contract
        INV-007: ended auctions are detected by elapsed duration OR below-minimum balance
    end note
